Wow where do I start!! My sisters graduated today!!!!! I am super super proud of the both of them. Words cannot even describe how proud they continue to make me. Not only did they graduate a semester early but also with honors (Cum Laude) and that is most definitely something to be proud of. Sky was co-captain this year over the Golden Girls, created some beautiful uniforms for the team, showed amazing leadership, one thing I can say about her is that she has most definitely left her mark! Star finished college while also starting her new life as a mom with her husband, closed on her first home, all while completing her degree. They are just getting started and I’m so blessed to be able to continue to see them grow. It’s only the beginning. @sweet_reflection @sweet__reflection 👩‍🎓😍🎓❤️
